### EXISTING STRUCTURES
No new structures were created in the latest steps. The agent focused on resource extraction and inventory management.

### ERROR TIPS
#### Errors when inserting into full containers
- Ensure the target container has sufficient space before attempting to insert items. Check the container's current inventory and capacity.
- If the container is full, either empty it or use another container with available space.

#### Repeated attempts to insert into full containers
- Avoid repeatedly attempting to insert items into a full container. This wastes time and resources. Instead, check the container's status once and take appropriate action.

### NAMESPACE
No new utility functions or variables were defined in the latest steps.
